lead_paragraph: A third successive clean sheet proved the high point of Saturday's win in the Dutch league for PSV Eindhoven coach Philip Cocu as his team prepare to host Atletico Madrid in the Champions League on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Clean Sheet Boosts PSV Ahead of Champions League Tie
